highlights.text: Number_i has the most spots on Viral Songs Japan. “未確認領域” is the highest at #10.
“BON” by Number_i has been on Viral Songs Japan the longest, at 466 days straight.
“you are beautiful in love” by Kimigasounarabokuhakou is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Japan at #4.
“真実” by Eikichi Yazawa is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Japan, up 20 spots at #60.
